signatureAbility.signatureDescription: Defenders with this ability can reach out of engaged blocks to tackle or sack nearby ballcarriers.
Defenders with this ability force more catch tackle knockouts in man-to-man versus short routes less than 10 yards from LoS
Defenders with this ability have higher chance to catch uncontested interceptions, and they have unlimited stamina on the return (until using a special move or breaking a tackle).
Players with this ability have an increased chance to catch passes that have been tipped into the air.
Defenders with this ability force more catch knockouts and react quicker in deep zone coverage, 20+ yards from the LoS and outside the hash marks.
RAC receivers fight for every possible yard after making a catch. When they enter the zone, this ability increases their success rate on RAC catches against single coverage.
Receivers with this ability catch more consistently while catching passes less than 10 yards from the LoS, outside the numbers
After securing a RAC catch, ballcarriers with this ability can quickly shift momentum, change direction, and turn the corner without sacrificing speed.
Ballcarriers with this ability have steerable juke animations.
Passers with this ability have perfect accuracy on all throws outside the numbers (except on high/low throws).
Passers with this ability have a reduced chance to be impacted by throw penalties caused by defensive pressure while their feet are set in the pocket
Midway through the fourth quarter in close games, players with this ability can easily enter (and remain in) the Zone.
Players with this ability will recover from the effects of Wear and Tear and fatigue at an increased rate between plays.
Blockers with this ability will frequently attempt and win impact blocks against linebackers and defensive backs when playing as a lineman or fullback.
